{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0c7b586c32","title":"对民兵工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1c46dc5cc","index":0,"year":1965,"month":4,"day":21,"articleId":"0c7b586c32"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7454c88684","type":"title","text":"对民兵工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32"},{"id":"67c54c5ef2","type":"paragraph","text":"对民兵工作的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32"},{"id":"3be7bc557d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32"},{"id":"fa6b376bbc","type":"paragraph","text":"1965.04.21","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32"},{"id":"366104b2f1","type":"paragraph","text":"搞四清，要把民兵搞好。首先要落实组织，有没有队长、班长，组织起来没有？首先是有没有，然后讲政治，不要地、富、反、坏之类，要贫下中农，中农子弟进步的也可以要。地富子女中进步的也可以。真打起来他们会分化的，一部分组织维持会，插白旗，杀共产党，一部分跟我们走。地主富农、资本家也会分化，不会全部跟敌人的。是要争取多数，孤立少数，不然就要失败。利用矛盾，争取多数孤立少数，各个击破。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32"},{"id":"c3f19cfc22","type":"paragraph","text":"民兵，第一是组织，第二是政治，第三是军事。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32"}],"page":{"id":"3bac854b85","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0c7b586c32","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}